<br>
and damn, enough bitching about mages.<br>
<br>
Nukes - God we're damn comparable, 700ish at 53 with char(unless char's 52, i can't recall).  450 and super fast cast with scars of sigil.  machine gun those out if ya want.<br>
<br>
dmg wise, our nukes + pets we outdmg any-@#%$-one in a standard group(well other than rogue, they're insane).  get 54/60 water pet, put it to mob's back, and let it loose.  there is no wizard or druid or anyone that can keep the nukes pumping to provide anywhere near the dmg were gonna do with some nukes and pet.  they'd get aggroed, summoned, and beat on.<br>
<br>
as per Soloing i've soloed most of my lvls from 1-56.  Though i have spent quite a bit of time in groups recently, and did group as i was lvling up.  we can solo fine, which many classes can't.  Those that can solo really well, better than us,  arn't as needed in a group, or raid.<br>
<br>
don't bitch about our spells please.  we have good nukes, awesome pets, nice DS's, and the Mala line, not to mention CoH/mod rods.<br>
<br>
and btw, it's 225 dmg, not 255.<br>
