<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Oh really? Wow, if you hadn't tell me that, I wouldn't know!!! I actually thought the GMs were the makers of the game. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
