<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> You call that balance?? Go over your own list of what we can do and what Druids can do. Go over it carefully and if you tell me that all classes are balanced again<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
Ok, I will, the game is balanced in non-raid situations.  The druid class is considered &quot;the jack of all trades.&quot;  Transportation, damage, healing, buffing, etc.  However, they're not the best at any of it, except transportation which they share with wizards.  So on raids they're pretty pointless cause you can get other classes that are especially good in that department.<br>
<br>
